{"tid":275988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果推蝗語不遺餘力","createTime":"2017-06-08T12:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T12:42:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da172d733610d3903cd9e2e244a88481fe2ded12","tid":275988,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"原文轉自膠登：<a href=\"http://m.hkgalden.com/view/385609/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgalden.com%2Fview%2F385609%2Fpage%2F1&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IomMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=305ffc6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgalden.com/view/385609/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果表面反共，內裏就文化殖民香港。<br />\n<br />\n成立廿幾年，表面一套反共，內心支那帝國觀，硬推垃圾文化世世代代攞你香港命...<br />\n<br />\n其他媒體因為媚共而自動被絕緣，推銷蝗語此路不通，但蘋果就可以用反共光環做解手軍做唔到嘅事<br />\n將你哋啲文化獨特性去稜磨角，模糊雙方分別，達至敵我不分來完成「一家親」同化目的。<br />\n<br />\n新一代香港人飲「蘋果奶水」或其他受洗禮奶水大，對呢類大頭b 奶水只有無抗拒乖乖接受嘅自然反應，其破壞力遠遠大過佔港解放軍武力鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n劣質文化詞如「上馬」、「人員」、「看齊」、「打造」、「部」、「反映」、「執行官」、「對」、「天」...等都變成港人日常用詞。<br />\n<br />\n標題到內文都係「上馬」<br />\n<br />\n新空管系統崩潰　下月硬上馬<br />\n<br />\n2016年10月30日<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161030/19816782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161030%2F19816782&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IomMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=db9a7da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161030%2F19816782&h=5c822a85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161030/19816782</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港人用港語<br />\n向滿口(州)胡言say no!"}]}